OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has been found not
OL,7,Fguilty of the manslaughter of his wife
OL,8,Fwho took her own life.
OL,10,FChristopher Trybus, of Swindon,
OL,11,FWiltshire, was cleared by a jury at
OL,12,FWinchester Crown Court of causing the
OL,13,Fdeath of 34-year-old Tarryn Baird, who
OL,14,Fdied in November 2017.
OL,16,FHe was also acquitted of two charges
OL,17,Fof rape against her and a count of
OL,18,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
