OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FThe prosecution had alleged that Mr
OL,7,FTrybus controlled Ms Baird through
OL,8,Fusing and threatening violence towards
OL,9,Fher, sexually assaulting her,
OL,10,Fmonitoring her whereabouts, limiting
OL,11,Fher access to finance, threatening to
OL,12,Freveal private information to her
OL,13,Ffamily and isolating her from her
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FHe was also accused of using a belt to
OL,17,Fchoke her and strangling her during
OL,18,Fsex causing her to pass out.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Mr Trybus, who ran an
OL,7,FIT company, said that he travelled
OL,8,Fabroad frequently for work and was out
OL,9,Fof the country on the days of several
OL,10,Fof the allegations.
OL,12,FHe also said he believed his wife had
OL,13,Fmental health issues due to post-
OL,14,Ftraumatic stress disorder (PTSD).
OL,16,FThe chairman of the jury of seven
OL,17,Fwomen and five men announced the
OL,18,Fverdicts to a hushed courtroom
OL,19,Ffollowing their 40 hours and eight
OL,20,Fminutes of deliberations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FThe defendant, dressed in a grey suit,
OL,7,Fblue shirt and dark tie loose at the
OL,8,Fcollar, looked up at the ceiling and
OL,9,Fburst into tears as the verdicts were
OL,10,Fannounced with cries of relief also
OL,11,Fheard from the public gallery.
OL,13,FOutside court, Mr Trybus hugged his
OL,14,Fcurrent wife Bea, who he married in
OL,15,FAugust 2024, with both of them in
OL,16,Ftears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FThe judge, Mr Justice Linden, thanked
OL,7,Fthe jurors for their service and told
OL,8,Fthem: "It was a difficult and sad case
OL,9,Fand the stakes were high for the
OL,10,Ffamilies involved so we understand
OL,11,Fyour task has not been an easy one and
OL,12,Fno-one should underestimate your role
OL,13,Fin these proceedings."
OL,15,FThe trial heard that Ms Baird was
OL,16,Fdiagnosed as probably suffering from
OL,17,Fpost traumatic stress disorder (PTSD)
OL,18,Fafter she witnessed violent car-
OL,19,Fjackings in South Africa where she and
OL,20,Fthe defendant grew up.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,FThe couple moved to the UK in 2007 and
OL,7,Fmarried in 2009 but an attempted
OL,8,Fburglary in 2015 appears to have
OL,9,Ftriggered Ms Baird's mental health
OL,10,Fissues including anxiety and
OL,11,Fdepression leading her to seek help
OL,12,Ffrom mental health professionals, the
OL,13,Fcourt heard.
OL,15,FDescribing how he felt about Ms Baird
OL,16,Fin light of the allegations, he told
OL,17,Fthe court: "It's such a complex
OL,18,Ffeeling, I loved her dearly and she
OL,19,Fhas gone and said all of these things.
OL,26,@yD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,F"At no point has this ever happened,
OL,7,Fit's such a mix of emotions, I am
OL,8,Fupset that she said these things but
OL,9,Fshe is not here so I can't be upset
OL,10,Fwith her, it's not something I can put
OL,11,Finto words."
OL,13,FSpeaking outside court and accompanied
OL,14,Fby his wife, Mr Trybus said: "After
OL,15,Fthree police investigations over the
OL,16,Fcourse of 10 years, I'm relieved that
OL,17,Fthe jury has carefully considered the
OL,18,Fevidence and reached the correct
OL,19,Fverdict today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]vD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,F"I want to thank my wife, my family,
OL,7,Fand my friends for their unwavering
OL,8,Fsupport ` and my legal team for their
OL,9,Fhard work and dedication throughout
OL,10,Fthe process.
OL,12,F"This has had a profound impact on my
OL,13,Flife and on those closest to me. It's
OL,14,Fbeen an incredibly difficult
OL,15,Fexperience.
OL,17,F"I would also like to acknowledge that
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse is a very real and
OL,19,Fserious issue, and victims must always
OL,20,Fbe supported.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776967869
OL,3,CMan cleared of manslaughter of wife
OL,4,Cwho took her own life
OL,6,F"Right now, I'll focus on moving
OL,7,Fforward and rebuilding my life with my
OL,8,Ffamily."
OL,10,FWhen he was asked if he had a message
OL,11,Ffor Ms Baird's family, he replied:
OL,12,F"No."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]tD@AOUtD@EO]
